questions_and_answers.question: What are the supported machine learning providers for model evaluations?
questions_and_answers.answer: Watson Machine Learning, Azure ML Studio, Azure ML Service, AWS SageMaker, and Custom (with equivalent functionality to Watson Machine Learning)
